        <Parent_String>daguerreotype (process) [300053530], direct positive processes [300133319], photographic processes [300133268], photography and photographic processes and techniques [300149146], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
